```js
class UserCard extends HTMLElement {
  constructor() {
    super();
    const shadow = this.attachShadow({ mode: 'open' });
    shadow.innerHTML = `
      <style>
        .card { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; }
      </style>
      <div class="card"><slot></slot></div>`;
  }
}
```

customElements.define('user-card', UserCard);
```

Usage:

