## Step 4: Batch Payouts

ts
@Scheduled('0 2 * * MON') // Every Monday at 02:00 UTC
async runWeeklyPayout() {
  const pending = await this.commissionRepo.find({ status: 'PENDING' });
  const batches = this.groupByAgent(pending);
  for (const [agentId, commissions] of Object.entries(batches)) {
    const total = commissions.reduce((sum, c) => sum + Number(c.amount), 0);
    await this.paymentProvider.transfer(agentId, total);
    await this.commissionRepo.update({ id: In(commissions.map(c => c.id)) }, { status: 'PAID' });
  }
}

A scheduled job aggregates pending commissions, triggers the external payment provider, and updates the ledger status.

